{"title":"塞娜的颂歌","date":"2019-12-21T17:38:16.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Dec 22, 2019","L":"12/22/2019","MM-DD":"12-22"},"thumbnail":"https://i.loli.net/2019/12/22/xnEuXeK9cQGrYpi.jpg","link":"2019/12/22/塞娜的颂歌","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-02-10T17:00:41.449Z","content":"<p>巨石陨落<br>\n在空中崩碎成沙<br>\n幻影斑驳<br>\n模糊可辨</p>\n<p>颤颤轻语<br>\n喃喃吟咏<br>\n是友也是敌</p>\n<p>每一具土灰都在挣扎<br>\n无声的狰狞<br>\n伸出残骨空捉<br>\n双脚已经在鲜红中凝固</p>\n<p>击落的提尔锋闪耀着蓝光<br>\n失落之人还在呼唤</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>*2019.12.22 凌晨<br>\n<em>上海 大雨倾盆</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n","prev":{"title":"小世界的管理者","link":"2019/12/30/小世界的管理者"},"next":{"title":"飘","link":"2019/12/20/飘"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2019/12/22/塞娜的颂歌/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"白桦树下的人","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"February 11, 2020"}}